TROUBLE SHOOTING

If you see this error:
pi@raspberrypi ~/pi-examples $ sudo ./spi_max1187
Raspberry Pi wiringPi SPI test program, max144:chan=0  clk/kHz=512 bufLen/kB=0
Unable to open SPI device: No such file or directory

DO just once:
gpio load spi

Then execute the test program
sudo ./spi_max187
